{"tid":278584,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"失眠故事","createTime":"2017-06-10T14:48:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T14:59:53.000Z","uid":34659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"68697efca9441d6ed9248eaf91f267f9805470f6","tid":278584,"uid":34659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T14:48:11.000Z","msg":"同大家講下我個故事啦<br />\n我兩年前追個師妺 中學 我追左佢兩年 直到前年十月學 校sports day得米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁就以為掂左 點知完全吾係嗰回事 系十日後已經綠左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我就當然之後冇理過佢 但系舊年佢生日我又<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  搵番佢之後又得知不久將來佢海外留學（今年年頭）我就非常之sad 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 頂左個綠帽膽青青除夕去佢樓下膝足長談<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 直到宜家佢出國半年我都放棄吾到佢 仲有聯繫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  尼一年期間雖然都有拍過一兩次拖 但係永遠冇第一次掂佢手嘅心跳感 自己好似逢場作戲一樣 其實我有冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2e42c2fd7e164be1e0f2ba9acc351bc07114438","tid":278584,"uid":34659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T14:51:41.000Z","msg":"完全系病態<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"298dc0243e0dfaf68f44e9e85facf48423831fe4","tid":278584,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T14:52:24.000Z","msg":"帽所謂啦屌 你都唔介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6bfe26fb2d2e4540c39c03fdc2567253259548f","tid":278584,"uid":34659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T14:54:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>帽所謂啦屌 你都唔介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n帽吾係咩大事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只系我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12be5af2045f6adce534a2a5ea3508708753e557","tid":278584,"uid":34659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T14:54:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>帽所謂啦屌 你都唔介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n只系我唸吾通自己啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"906c70df044c4f2a60111200883ed7447688a666","tid":278584,"uid":34659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T14:59:53.000Z","msg":"真系好頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}